## Critical Rules

- **2 tags per track** — Exactly 2 genre tags, never use "Cinematic" as tag
- **Living collections** — Use "collection" terminology, not "album"
- **OKLCH only** — Use OKLCH color tokens from globals.css, not hex
- **Typography** — Cinzel (headings), Poppins (body)

